task.summary: Default task

Add work on grouper
Grouper is fully functional for at least Action Value. Left to do is: - implement other features for data analysis - fix all .xlsx for Prob_RL task - Finish formatting code in main file - Start data analysis - Continue on with making this program expandable

Finish prelim work on grouper
Can assemble all action value and RL_Prob data. If any additional calculated columns are necessary, they can be added to the utils.py file.

Add definitions for groups
Add function in utils to define which group each subject belongs to. Also start on some formatting for output excel
Almost complete grouper; need output formatting fix

Added new output column and fixed choice made
Choice made was actually unnecessary, so it was removed from utils. Some input columns were changed, and it was determined that in order to correctly get the max amount of reversals made, I needed to use 'RestCount' which denotes how many trials were left in the task. When this was 0, that denotes the highest number of reversals, since everything after is just the program running through remaining trials once each.

Complete count of reversals in task
Number of reversal counts have been completed for both tasks, the function is complete in unils.
